TI Cystic fibrosis: a not-so-fatal disease.
SO Pediatr-Clin-North-Am. 1974 Nov. 21(4). P 935-50. (REVIEW).
MJ CYSTIC-FIBROSIS: th.
MN ADOLESCENCE.  ADULT.  CHILD.  CHILD-PRESCHOOL.
   CYSTIC-FIBROSIS: di, mo, co.  DIET-THERAPY.  DIETARY-FATS: ad.
